    "body": "p2p-enabled needs to be set for any p2p options to be looked at, but having said that, if p2p-enabled is not set, we don't want to fail to start, and its likely to not be worth the effort of raising log errors, because it's actually expected a lot of the time (like in devops scenarios).\n\nThere aren't any other obvious dependencies, because all other dependencies have predefined default values that are sensible.",
